% Krishna Lunch Salad Dressing
% Krishna Lunch at UF

# Acquire

*   1/2 cup powdered almonds
*   1/2 cup nutritional yeast
*   1/2 cup sunflower or safflower oil
*   3/4 cup water (add more later if it's too thick)
*   1 tbsp Bragg liquid aminos (alternatively: soy sauce)
*   1/6 tsp asafoetida powder (strong stuff)

# Prepare

2.  Put the ingredients into a blender, and blend for 30 seconds.
3.  Refrigerate. (Note: the dressing will thicken with refrigeration.)
